# Plugin Conventions

- Plugin owns ALL data structures — CPTs, ACF field groups, admin columns
- Register ACF fields programmatically via `acf_add_local_field_group()`
- Check for ACF dependency and show admin notice if missing
- Define constants: `JJBBQ_PLUGIN_PATH`, `JJBBQ_PLUGIN_URL`, `JJBBQ_VERSION`
- Helper functions are callable by the theme (e.g., `jjbbq_get_next_event()`)
- Hook CPT registration to `init` action
- Seed data function runs only once (checked via `get_option('jjbbq_seeded')`)
